<article class="row hentry post-255193 to4_article_post type-to4_article_post status-publish has-post-thumbnail category-news-analysis tag-bay-of-pigs tag-cuba-embargo tag-fidel-castro tag-international-law tag-lawsuits tag-marco-rubio tag-nationalization tag-sanctions section-politics-and-elections primary_topic-politics series-human-rights-and-global-wrongs" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/AnalysisNewsArticle">
