<div class='categories'>
<a href='https://truthout.org/category/news-analysis/' rel='category' class='news-analysis'>News Analysis</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="">
<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/human-rights-hypocrisy-us-criticizes-cuba/">Human Rights Hypocrisy: US Criticizes Cuba</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">President Obama should close Guantanamo and return it to Cuba.</div>
</div>
</div>
